Enjoy hot, mouth-watering cinnamon rolls before at the tailgate party, or delicious cornbread at deer camp with the Portable Outdoor Oven. So bring your favorite recipes because your outdoor cooking possibilities have just expanded. This oven will give you the ability to bake in temperatures up to 350° F using a 9 x 13 pan. When you’re camping with the Portable Outdoor Oven you can enjoy delicious, hot blueberry muffins in the morning and rich chocolate brownies in the evening. This oven is also perfect for fresh bread, enchiladas and more. Because of its portability it is great to have on hand for emergency preparedness.
